Class Interleaving

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.search.Search
      • gov.nasa.jpf.search.heuristic.HeuristicSearch

          • gov.nasa.jpf.search.heuristic.Interleaving

  • public class Interleaving
extends SimplePriorityHeuristic
    Heuristic to maximize thread interleavings. It is particularly good at flushing out concurrency errors, since it schedules different threads as much as possible.
